subject: Luge Racing
Nordic Combined (Winter Sport Event)
lead_paragraph: Patric Leitner and Alexander Resch of Germany won their first World Cup luge doubles race of the season in Koenigssee, Germany. They finished in 1:34.616 for their 32nd overall win.
